{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id4d34a35b-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20901"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"20901"},"text":"§ 20901.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Declaration of purpose","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In order to protect the public from sex offenders and offenders against children, and in response to the vicious attacks by violent predators against the victims listed below, Congress in this chapter establishes a comprehensive national system for the registration of those offenders:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d34a35c-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20901/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Jacob Wetterling, who was 11 years old, was abducted in 1989 in Minnesota, and remains missing.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d34a35d-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20901/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Megan Nicole Kanka, who was 7 years old, was abducted, sexually assaulted, and murdered in 1994, in New Jersey.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d34a35e-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20901/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Pam Lychner, who was 31 years old, was attacked by a career offender in Houston, Texas.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d34a35f-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20901/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Jetseta Gage, who was 10 years old, was kidnapped, sexually assaulted, and murdered in 2005, in Cedar Rapids, Iowa.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d34a360-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20901/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Dru Sjodin, who was 22 years old, was sexually assaulted and murdered in 2003, in North Dakota.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d34a361-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20901/6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6"},"text":"(6)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Jessica Lunsford, who was 9 years old, was abducted, sexually assaulted, buried alive, and murdered in 2005, in Homosassa, Florida.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d34a362-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20901/7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"7"},"text":"(7)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Sarah Lunde, who was 13 years old, was strangled and murdered in 2005, in Ruskin, Florida.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d34a363-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20901/8"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"8"},"text":"(8)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Amie Zyla, who was 8 years old, was sexually assaulted in 1996 by a juvenile offender in Waukesha, Wisconsin, and has become an advocate for child victims and protection of children from juvenile sex offenders.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d34a364-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20901/9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"9"},"text":"(9)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Christy Ann Fornoff, who was 13 years old, was abducted, sexually assaulted, and murdered in 1984, in Tempe, Arizona.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d34a365-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20901/10"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"10"},"text":"(10)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Alexandra Nicole Zapp, who was 30 years old, was brutally attacked and murdered in a public restroom by a repeat sex offender in 2002, in Bridgewater, Massachusetts.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d34a366-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20901/11"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"11"},"text":"(11)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Polly Klaas, who was 12 years old, was abducted, sexually assaulted, and murdered in 1993 by a career offender in California.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d34a367-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20901/12"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"12"},"text":"(12)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Jimmy Ryce, who was 9 years old, was kidnapped and murdered in Florida on ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1995-09-11"},"text":"September 11, 1995","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4d34a368-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s20901/13"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"13"},"text":"(13)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Carlie Brucia, who was 11 years old, was abducted an